name: NetworkLookup

”nslookup amazon.com”
”Alexa, ask network lookup to test amazon.com”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: network lookup
des:
It's a very handy tool to check the status of your web application, think if you are at home and wants to know the health status of your web application.

Wake word network lookup

You can test by saying "look www.amazon.com" or "nslookup amazon.com" to get the IP address of the websites.

You can say "status of amazon.com" to get the HTTP Status code of the mentioned website.

Easy right :)
